1130
01:05:38.932 --> 01:05:39.272
So this

1131
01:05:40.612 --> 01:05:44.452
already brings me to the end, showing the perspective of

1132
01:05:44.512 --> 01:05:48.172
the European or EU way of

1133
01:05:48.412 --> 01:05:52.292
using precision oncology data for precision medicine.

1134
01:05:52.332 --> 01:05:55.932
The lesson we have learned, particularly from the ACIR Genie, is

1135
01:05:55.972 --> 01:05:59.652
that Genie has shown that multi-institutional data sharing is feasible,

1136
01:06:00.372 --> 01:06:04.272
and with these layers of data sharing and the Candle project,

1137
01:06:04.352 --> 01:06:07.492
the Uncan project, the EU is now trying to scale this up to

1138
01:06:08.992 --> 01:06:12.412
up to 20 nations. The second lesson is that the

1139
01:06:12.512 --> 01:06:15.322
