1142
01:06:23.192 --> 01:06:26.072
constant flow of data coming directly from the

1143
01:06:27.032 --> 01:06:30.681
medical doctors, and this creates also the operational infrastructure for

1144
01:06:30.752 --> 01:06:34.492
patient care. And last but not least, cBioPortal is a very good

1145
01:06:34.532 --> 01:06:38.352
foundation you can build on. You can extend this data, bring it into patient care,

1146
01:06:38.432 --> 01:06:42.192
for example, adapt it for clinical routine, and really enlarge

1147
01:06:42.332 --> 01:06:44.032
patient care with that. And

1148
01:06:44.912 --> 01:06:48.772
through that, I hope I could show that we have the basis with the

1149
01:06:48.832 --> 01:06:52.032
AC Genie data model, which provides the standards,

1150
01:06:52.632 --> 01:06:56.272
and the EU tries to bring federated infrastructure.

1151
01:06:56.712 --> 01:06:58.752
And also, we are on the local level.

1152
01:06:59.212 --> 01:07:02.796
We perform local adaptation to make-This idea

1153
01:07:02.816 --> 01:07:06.516
clinical actionably. And with that, I think one can enable this

1154
01:07:06.656 --> 01:07:10.416
really transatlantic real-world evidence at a large scale for better

1155
01:07:10.456 --> 01:07:11.056
patient care.

1156
01:07:11.996 --> 01:07:15.916
So with that, I would like to acknowledge the people

1157
01:07:15.936 --> 01:07:16.956
that are working on this

